@startuml
title TestForge - Ciclo de Vida da RecordingSession

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Black
  FontColor Black
}

[*] --> CREATED : create_session

state CREATED
state VALIDATING_INPUT
state WORKSPACE_READY
state BROWSER_STARTING
state BROWSER_READY
state INITIAL_FINGERPRINTING
state INSTRUMENTING_PAGE
state RECORDING_ACTIVE
state RECORDING_PAUSED
state CHECKPOINT_CREATED
state FINALIZING_RECORDING
state RAW_SESSION_SAVED
state VALIDATING_RECORDING
state RECORDING_VALID
state RECORDING_REPAIRABLE
state RECORDING_INVALID
state NORMALIZING
state NORMALIZED
state SCRIPT_GENERATED
state DIAGNOSTIC_EXECUTION
state CURATION_REQUIRED
state STABILIZATION_REQUIRED
state FINALIZED
state FAILED

CREATED --> VALIDATING_INPUT : start_recording_command / receive_parameters

VALIDATING_INPUT --> WORKSPACE_READY : input_valid / create_output_slug_structure
VALIDATING_INPUT --> FAILED : input_invalid / persist_validation_error

WORKSPACE_READY --> BROWSER_STARTING : workspace_created / start_playwright

BROWSER_STARTING --> BROWSER_READY : browser_started / create_browser_context
BROWSER_STARTING --> FAILED : browser_start_failed / persist_startup_error

BROWSER_READY --> INITIAL_FINGERPRINTING : page_ready / navigate_to_endpoint_and_save_baseline

INITIAL_FINGERPRINTING --> INSTRUMENTING_PAGE : fingerprint_initial_saved / activate_technology_collectors
INITIAL_FINGERPRINTING --> FAILED : fingerprint_failed_unrecoverable / persist_fingerprint_error

INSTRUMENTING_PAGE --> RECORDING_ACTIVE : recorder_js_and_overlay_injected / start_enriched_capture
INSTRUMENTING_PAGE --> FAILED : instrumentation_failed_unrecoverable / persist_instrumentation_error

RECORDING_ACTIVE --> RECORDING_PAUSED : pause_requested / suspend_event_capture
RECORDING_PAUSED --> RECORDING_ACTIVE : resume_requested / resume_event_capture

RECORDING_ACTIVE --> CHECKPOINT_CREATED : checkpoint_requested_or_assert_hint_detected / persist_checkpoint
CHECKPOINT_CREATED --> RECORDING_ACTIVE : checkpoint_saved / continue_recording

RECORDING_ACTIVE --> FINALIZING_RECORDING : finish_requested / flush_pending_events
RECORDING_PAUSED --> FINALIZING_RECORDING : finish_requested / flush_pending_events

' BUG-019: browser fechado pelo usuário dispara finish_requested
RECORDING_ACTIVE --> FINALIZING_RECORDING : browser_closed / page.on("close")→finish_requested
note on link
  BUG-019: page.on("close") detectado em collect_step.
  is_closed() verificado no início de cada iteração (100ms).
  Pacing via time.sleep(0.1) — não wait_for_timeout (BUG-021).
  Recorder.finish() pula collect_final se is_closed()==True.
  BrowserManager.close() em try/except para browser já fechado.
end note

' BUG-018: full-page navigation preserva estado recording_active
RECORDING_ACTIVE --> RECORDING_ACTIVE : full_page_navigation / sessionStorage.__tfRecordingActive persiste
note on link
  BUG-018: page.add_init_script() reinjeta OVERLAY_JS em toda
  full-page navigation. window.var é resetado, mas
  sessionStorage.getItem('__tfRecordingActive') === 'true'
  permite restaurar state='recording' automaticamente.
end note

FINALIZING_RECORDING --> RAW_SESSION_SAVED : pending_events_collected / save_session_raw_and_fingerprint_final
FINALIZING_RECORDING --> FAILED : finalize_failed_unrecoverable / persist_finalize_error

RAW_SESSION_SAVED --> VALIDATING_RECORDING : raw_session_saved / validate_recording_integrity

VALIDATING_RECORDING --> RECORDING_VALID : validation_passed / mark_ready_for_normalization
VALIDATING_RECORDING --> RECORDING_REPAIRABLE : validation_found_repairable_gaps / run_auto_repair
VALIDATING_RECORDING --> RECORDING_INVALID : validation_failed_insufficient_evidence / generate_insufficient_recording_report

RECORDING_REPAIRABLE --> VALIDATING_RECORDING : auto_repair_applied / revalidate_recording
RECORDING_REPAIRABLE --> RECORDING_INVALID : auto_repair_failed / preserve_repair_evidence

RECORDING_INVALID --> FAILED : invalid_recording_confirmed / stop_pipeline

RECORDING_VALID --> NORMALIZING : recording_valid / parse_and_normalize_steps

NORMALIZING --> NORMALIZED : normalization_completed / save_session_normalized_and_steps
NORMALIZING --> FAILED : normalization_failed_unrecoverable / persist_normalization_error

NORMALIZED --> SCRIPT_GENERATED : generate_script_v0 / save_script_metadata

SCRIPT_GENERATED --> DIAGNOSTIC_EXECUTION : script_v0_created / execute_diagnostic_run

DIAGNOSTIC_EXECUTION --> STABILIZATION_REQUIRED : script_passed / promote_to_stabilization
DIAGNOSTIC_EXECUTION --> CURATION_REQUIRED : script_failed / build_failure_signature
DIAGNOSTIC_EXECUTION --> FAILED : diagnostic_execution_error_unrecoverable / persist_run_error

CURATION_REQUIRED --> DIAGNOSTIC_EXECUTION : patch_validated_and_applied / rerun_checkpoint_or_script
CURATION_REQUIRED --> FAILED : curation_unresolved_limit_exceeded / persist_unresolved_report

STABILIZATION_REQUIRED --> FINALIZED : stabilization_passed / build_final_artifacts
STABILIZATION_REQUIRED --> CURATION_REQUIRED : stabilization_failed / classify_new_failure
STABILIZATION_REQUIRED --> FAILED : stabilization_error_unrecoverable / persist_stabilization_error

FINALIZED --> [*] : final_artifacts_ready
FAILED --> [*] : session_closed_with_error

CREATED --> FAILED : unrecoverable_error
WORKSPACE_READY --> FAILED : unrecoverable_error
BROWSER_READY --> FAILED : unrecoverable_error
RECORDING_ACTIVE --> FAILED : unrecoverable_error
RECORDING_PAUSED --> FAILED : unrecoverable_error
CHECKPOINT_CREATED --> FAILED : unrecoverable_error
RAW_SESSION_SAVED --> FAILED : unrecoverable_error
RECORDING_VALID --> FAILED : unrecoverable_error
NORMALIZED --> FAILED : unrecoverable_error
SCRIPT_GENERATED --> FAILED : unrecoverable_error
CURATION_REQUIRED --> FAILED : unrecoverable_error
STABILIZATION_REQUIRED --> FAILED : unrecoverable_error

note right of RECORDING_REPAIRABLE
  RECORDING_REPAIRABLE indica que a gravação possui
  inconsistências corrigíveis, como gaps pequenos de
  timestamp, ordenação de eventos, referências ausentes
  ou artefatos incrementais incompletos.

  A sessão não avança para normalização enquanto a
  autocorreção não for aplicada e a gravação não for
  validada novamente.
end note

note right of CURATION_REQUIRED
  CURATION_REQUIRED ocorre quando o script_v0.py falha
  na execução diagnóstica.

  A curadoria deve reutilizar a gravação e as evidências
  originais: DOM, rede, console, screenshots, frames,
  shadow DOM, storage, selector_candidates e fingerprints.

  O LLM não é primeira opção; antes dele são usadas
  estratégias determinísticas e agentes especializados.
end note

note right of STABILIZATION_REQUIRED
  STABILIZATION_REQUIRED ocorre quando o script passa
  na execução diagnóstica, mas ainda precisa ser tornado
  robusto, determinístico e finalizável.

  Nesta fase devem ser consolidados locators, healing_rules,
  massa de teste separada, remoção de sleeps frágeis e
  execução de rodadas limpas antes do FINALIZED.
end note

' BUG-020: Referências a componentes reais (BUG-007–BUG-014)
note as N_BUG020
  Componentes relevantes neste ciclo de vida:
  - Recorder: gerencia estados RECORDING_ACTIVE→FINALIZING_RECORDING
  - RecorderOverlay: injeta OVERLAY_JS via page.add_init_script()
    window.__tfRecordingActive + sessionStorage (BUG-018)
  - BrowserManager: launch() usa navigation_timeout_ms (BUG-007)
    BrowserConfig.navigation_timeout_ms=60000 padrão
  - DebugLogger: singleton instrumentado em cada transição de estado
    configure(slug, output_dir, debug_mode) chamado em BROWSER_STARTING
end note

@enduml
